casebody.data:
Alberto Francisco RUIZ, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
The STATE of Florida, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D18-1478 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. OCTOBER 04, 2018 ROTHENBERG, C.J., and LAGOA and SCALES, JJ., concur.

Following review of the petition for writ of habeas corpus, and the response and reply thereto, it is ordered that said petition is hereby denied.
